title: Week 1 preview & QB rankings
itunes:title: Week 1 preview & QB rankings
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler - recap the NFL season opener between the New England Patriots and the Pittsburgh Steelers. Then, the heroes go game-by-game breaking down each Week 1 matchup. Plus, NFL Media's Andrew Siciliano drops by to talk Week 1 quarterback rankings.
